#{127}{}{[He aims at the nearest ball] Well, here we are - in Reno, the city spared by Lady Luck. There's satisfaction for every kind of thirst here. Have you broken the bank at any of the casinos yet? Or are you the type that refuses to risk anything on a game of chance?}
{127}{}{[他瞄准最近的球]好吧，我们到了――在雷诺，幸运女神保佑的城市。这里的每一种干渴都能得到满足。你在任何一家赌场破了银行吗？或者你是那种拒绝冒险的人？ -- [He aims at the nearest ball] Well, here we are - in Reno, the city spared by Lady Luck. There's satisfaction for every kind of thirst here. Have you broken the bank at any of the casinos yet? Or are you the type that refuses to risk anything on a game of chance?}
#{128}{}{I might gamble, but I only bet what I can afford.}
