#{142}{}{[He sighs] One has to be careful with women. Barker, Dillinger... A lot of great men have been laid low by this sort of thing. [he shoots] Ha! I learned that trick shot from... Well, it doesn't matter. He's just another one of Reno's beggars now.}
{142}{}{[他叹息]一个人必须小心对待女人。巴克，迪林杰。。。很多伟人都被这种事贬低了。[他开枪]哈！我是从……学来这个把戏的。。。好吧，没关系。他现在只是雷诺的另一个乞丐。 -- [He sighs] One has to be careful with women. Barker, Dillinger... A lot of great men have been laid low by this sort of thing. [he shoots] Ha! I learned that trick shot from... Well, it doesn't matter. He's just another one of Reno's beggars now.}
